    {
      "text": "Shiroi Ringu he, full title Joshi Puroresu Story: Shiroi Ringu he: Twinkle Little Star (女子プロレスSTORY 白いリングへ Twinkle Little Star; Women's Pro Wrestling Story: To the White Ring: Twinkle Little Star), is a professional wrestling video game for the Super Famicom that was released on December 27, 1995. Popular female Japanese professional wrestlers like Shinobu Kandori and Noriyo Tateno appear in this game.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "『白いリングへ』は、ポニーキャニオンから発売された日本のゲームソフト。正式名称は『女子プロレスSTORY 白いリングへ Twinkle Little Star』。",
